title: Quick Web Photo Resizer 2.4.0.0.exe
description: Normally, you need to resize your digital photos or other images before uploading them to the Web or sending via e-mail. This program offers an ingenious way of processing your images. You simply select a resizing scheme and drag images to the program&#039;s window. The program will automatically choose a JPEG Quality/Compression level for each image to best fit the file size and dimensions that you selected.
